snippet.title: Boomerang Jack - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist and Play Demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2010010/Boomerang_Jack/

Slash 'n dash through lightning-fast boomerang combat, epic bosses and over-the-top acrobatics. Unlock and master abilities like bullet-time kicks and telekinetic tornadoes. Plunge into a shrouded realm of primordial threats and untapped power in this swashbuckling pirate adventure.

Follow us on twitter: https://twitter.com/boomjackgame
